<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WHEN MOTHERS OF SALEM</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Salem khuo a nute'n,
 A chateu Isu kawma;
 A puih lai un sinsakte chun,
 Amau chu ana hawu;
 Mahleh a taih mau in Isu'n,
 A na mu a, Aw nem takin;
 &quot;Naupangte ka kawma-
 Hung ding phal un&quot; tin.

[V2]
 2. &quot;Amau kipahpih in,
 Ka angsungah pawm ingka;
 Nawhmang kiuin, zehaw ding hin,
 A Belampuu hi'ng ka;
 A lunggil teu ei piek u chun,
 Ka kawmah lopi'n um un au;
 Naupangte Ka kawmah,
 Hung ding phal un,&quot; ti'n.

[V3]
 3. Naupangte na lawp di'n,
 Hukampa a zainem hi;
 Mahleh A min he kha nailo,
 Sang tamtak a um ui;
 Bible a sim kha ngei puoi hi,
 Hukdampa thugen za dingin,
 &quot;Naupangte ka kawma hung ding phal un tin.&quot;

[V4]
 4. Namtin, chitin laka,
 Pathien thu awilote hin;
 Na thu awi mengu hen,
 A milim teu paihmang u hen;
 A lunggil uh salhvak inla,
 Hehpih Pathien na hih hilh in,
 Naupangte Na kawm lam zawt dan sinsak in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>416</hymn_number>
</song>